A simple client-server based chatting application for single or multiple clients using
sockets and multi threading module with the concept of 
Clients post messages on the GUI (created using simple Tkinter package). 
Messages posted by each client is shows to every other client connected to the server. 
Basically a chatroom system where every message is shows to everyone 
and all the messages are encoded between the devices 
This is a python program for peer-to-peer chat application, built as a 
class project for Computer Networks. It can communicate between peers 
without the need for a central server. The only requirement is to know the peer's 
network address in the form of IP and Port number.